{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01NcR3HpNGL53ySEnhPvinHp","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Specification: 008 User Profile\n2\t\n3\t## Meta\n4\t\n5\t| Field | Value |\n6\t|-------|-------|\n7\t| Status | Ready |\n8\t| Priority | P1 |\n9\t| Phase | 3 |\n10\t| NR_OF_TRIES | 23 |\n11\t\n12\t---\n13\t\n14\t## Overview\n15\t\n16\tPlayer profile system for TAUNT. Backend/API only ‚Äî no frontend work in this\n17\tspec. The profile is the player's identity on the platform: a username, avatar,\n18\taggregate stats, and transaction history. Wallets are never exposed publicly;\n19\tall external-facing lookups use a short user ID or username.\n20\t\n21\t**Iteration 1 (done):** Transaction history ledger + API.\n22\t\n23\t**Iteration 2 (this pass):** Player identity (profile record, username, avatar),\n24\taggregate stats, public lookup API, HEAT/points display slots (null until those\n25\tfeatures ship).\n26\t\n27\tNo on-chain footprint. No social accounts (X/Discord) ‚Äî deferred TBD.\n28\t\n29\t## User Stories\n30\t\n31\t- As a player, I want to see every game transaction tied to my wallet so I can\n32\t  track what I wagered, won, or lost.\n33\t- As a player, I want the list to update automatically after a game settles so\n34\t  I don't have to refresh.\n35\t- As a player, I want an auto-generated username when I sign up so I have an\n36\t  identity on the platform immediately.\n37\t- As a player, I want to change my username so I can personalize my identity,\n38\t  with a cooldown to prevent abuse.\n39\t- As a player, I want to see my aggregate stats (games played, wins, win rate,\n40\t  streaks) so I can track my performance.\n41\t- As another player, I want to look up someone by username or ID and see their\n42\t  public stats (games played, wins, win rate) without seeing their wallet or\n43\t  transaction history.\n44\t\n45\t---\n46\t\n47\t## Scope Alignment\n48\t\n49\t- **`docs/SCOPE.md` references**: Phase 3 ‚Äî \"Basic player profile/history from\n50\t  indexed data\"; Launch checklist ‚Äî \"Basic profile/history available and\n51\t  accurate\"\n52\t- **Scope status**: V1 In Scope\n53\t- **Phase boundary**: Phase 3\n54\t\n55\t## Required Context Files\n56\t\n57\t- `services/backend/src/db.ts` ‚Äî DB client & query functions\n58\t- `services/backend/src/worker/settle-tx.ts` ‚Äî settlement write path (coinflip + lord)\n59\t- `services/backend/src/worker/closecall-clock.ts` ‚Äî closecall settlement write path (settleRound function)\n60\t- `services/backend/src/routes/` ‚Äî existing route patterns"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"056dd687-a09d-4a16-94d1-459ad839de8f","uuid":"1f6c1d8b-96a2-411f-8d2a-8a488beed22c","timestamp":"2026-03-31T15:22:46.185Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/008-user-profile/spec.md","content":"# Specification: 008 User Profile\n\n## Meta\n\n| Field | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| Status | Ready |\n| Priority | P1 |\n| Phase | 3 |\n| NR_OF_TRIES | 23 |\n\n---\n\n## Overview\n\nPlayer profile system for TAUNT. Backend/API only ‚Äî no frontend work in this\nspec. The profile is the player's identity on the platform: a username, avatar,\naggregate stats, and transaction history. Wallets are never exposed publicly;\nall external-facing lookups use a short user ID or username.\n\n**Iteration 1 (done):** Transaction history ledger + API.\n\n**Iteration 2 (this pass):** Player identity (profile record, username, avatar),\naggregate stats, public lookup API, HEAT/points display slots (null until those\nfeatures ship).\n\nNo on-chain footprint. No social accounts (X/Discord) ‚Äî deferred TBD.\n\n## User Stories\n\n- As a player, I want to see every game transaction tied to my wallet so I can\n  track what I wagered, won, or lost.\n- As a player, I want the list to update automatically after a game settles so\n  I don't have to refresh.\n- As a player, I want an auto-generated username when I sign up so I have an\n  identity on the platform immediately.\n- As a player, I want to change my username so I can personalize my identity,\n  with a cooldown to prevent abuse.\n- As a player, I want to see my aggregate stats (games played, wins, win rate,\n  streaks) so I can track my performance.\n- As another player, I want to look up someone by username or ID and see their\n  public stats (games played, wins, win rate) without seeing their wallet or\n  transaction history.\n\n---\n\n## Scope Alignment\n\n- **`docs/SCOPE.md` references**: Phase 3 ‚Äî \"Basic player profile/history from\n  indexed data\"; Launch checklist ‚Äî \"Basic profile/history available and\n  accurate\"\n- **Scope status**: V1 In Scope\n- **Phase boundary**: Phase 3\n\n## Required Context Files\n\n- `services/backend/src/db.ts` ‚Äî DB client & query functions\n- `services/backend/src/worker/settle-tx.ts` ‚Äî settlement write path (coinflip + lord)\n- `services/backend/src/worker/closecall-clock.ts` ‚Äî closecall settlement write path (settleRound function)\n- `services/backend/src/routes/` ‚Äî existing route patterns","numLines":60,"startLine":1,"totalLines":684}}}
